      "text": "Mostly with you.\n\nI prefer to abstract pipelines into a series of a-la-carte optional jobs or steps.\n\nOr, better yet, make pipelines that just call a single script.\n\nIMO: The more complicated the YAML is to write, the worse the pipeline is.\n\nIf it's easy, it's good."
